lead_paragraph: Adam Scott put together back-to-back rounds of 68 and feels like he's really back in the swing of things as he heads into the weekend at the Australian PGA Championship four shots off the pace.

headline.print_headline: Dodt Leads Australian PGA, Adam Scott Within Striking Range
